WEBVTT

00:03:29.058 --> 00:03:30.172
Ular ko'pchilik bo'lgan

00:03:30.172 --> 00:03:32.342
va ularning ko'pi ingliz ayollariga 
uylangan.

00:03:32.342 --> 00:03:34.568
Shunday ekan, tez orada bir avlod 
ko'z oldida

00:03:34.568 --> 00:03:38.208
osonlashtirilgan ingliz tili asl 
ingliz tili bilan bir vaqtda foydalanila

00:03:38.208 --> 00:03:41.027
boshlandi, sal o'tib asl ingliz tilini 
unutishdi ham.

00:03:41.027 --> 00:03:43.703
Oldingi so'zlarni hech kim eslamasdi, 
masalan,

00:03:43.703 --> 00:03:44.871
'doors' o'rniga 'doora',

00:03:44.871 --> 00:03:47.033
va 'hands' o'rniga 'handa' deyilganini.

00:03:47.033 --> 00:03:48.864
Hozirda ko'plik ancha tushunarliroq,

00:03:48.864 --> 00:03:51.017
'teeth' kabi ba'zi saqlanib qolgan 
so'zlarni

00:03:51.017 --> 00:03:51.949
hisobga olmaganda.

00:03:51.949 --> 00:03:53.039
O'rganib qolishganlari

00:03:53.039 --> 00:03:55.394
sabab, ularni o'zgartirishdan ma'no 
ko'rishmagan.

00:03:55.394 --> 00:03:56.300
Xulosa shundayki,

00:03:56.300 --> 00:03:59.086
ingliz tili aslida siz o'ylagandan 
ko'ra mantiqiyroq.

00:03:59.086 --> 00:04:00.636
